ences==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{cite web|url=http://www.tribuneindia.com/2007/20070415/spectrum/art.htm |title=The Sunday Tribune - Spectrum |website=Tribuneindia.com |date= |accessdate=2016-11-12}}\n\n{{coord missing|Punjab (India)}}\n\n[[Category:Monuments and memorials in Punjab, India]]\n[[Category:Mughal architecture ]]\n[[Category:Fatehgarh Sahib district]]\n[[Category:Tourism in Punjab, India]]\n", "name_user": "Certes", "label": "safe", "comment": "Fix links to Punjab (viaWP:JWB)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tombs_of_Ustad-Shagird,_Sirhind"}
